{"tid":2411794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅與南韓外長通電話　反對以意識形態劃分陣營 盡早促成習近平訪韓","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T06:15:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1f57f7943007eb97bf8e9b3627e6491db7463c","tid":2411794,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅同南韓新任外長鄭義溶通電話。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，中方支持開放、包容的地區合作機制，反對以意識形態劃分陣營。王毅強調，中韓互為重要近鄰和戰略合作夥伴，兩國關係朝著實現共同發展、致力地區和平、攜手振興亞洲、促進世界繁榮的目標邁進。<br />\n<br />\n關於朝鮮半島局勢，王毅表示，各方應加強溝通協調，為維護半島和平穩定，實現半島無核化、建立半島永久和平機制兩大目標作出努力。鄭義溶表示韓方願意為推動重啟朝鮮半島和談，繼續發揮建設作用。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，雙方商定繼續保持溝通，在疫情趨於穩定後，盡早促成國家主席習近平訪韓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575947-20210217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575947-20210217.htm&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN22aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=494d426e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575947-20210217.htm&h=2937476e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575947-20210217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"000a24dae9fbc0eb35ce8c4a8066a831e390ed52","tid":2411794,"uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:56:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">實現共同發展、致力地區和平、攜手振興亞洲、促進世界繁榮的目標邁進<br />\n</span>日本做過啦你又唔鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc3452e9615e0bceda15b594b018e5d1aafa1a0","tid":2411794,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"睇黎南韓總統都唔會有好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cf5effdc99e02b691bfe7bf663fc2fd9c93117","tid":2411794,"uid":51583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"我宜家要黎訪問<br />\n快D安排"},{"pid":"4a983be8b5b21d8ce